  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Excellent hot and cold buffet breakfast</li>
<li>Buffet style evening meal featuring live cooking station in the '3 Seasons' restaurant. Choose from a variety of salads/starters/soups, main courses and desserts. </li>
<li>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included for half board guests </li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>A firm favourite of Inghams guests, this hotel offers high standards of comfort, service and cuisine. It has recently been completely renovated and enjoys some of the best views over <a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> and some of the best views towards the Matterhorn.</p>
<p>Inside you'll find a warm and inviting atmosphere, crackling open fire and plush armchairs. It's welcoming, traditional and homely but with splashes of luxury and grandness as well. The spa area is excellent with a big indoor swimming pool, two whirlpools and winter garden with fantastic views of the Matterhorn. </p>]]></description>
